00:15:02,270 --> 00:15:08,250
[Inside my own hangout, I discovered an old film camera.]

217
00:15:12,720 --> 00:15:18,740
[I made eye contact with an unfamiliar guy.]

218
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:34,170
[1. Greet him awkwardly.]
[2. Press the camera shutter.]

219
00:15:34,170 --> 00:15:36,200
[2. Press the camera shutter.]

220
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:49,980
Hi.

221
00:15:52,230 --> 00:15:53,790
Hi.

222
00:15:57,980 --> 00:15:59,230
[Would you like to move on to the next stage?]

223
00:15:59,230 --> 00:16:00,740
[Yes/No]

